  m_text: 'Ren is the consecutive line clear combo counter. If you stack the sides
    high enough and get lucky enough with your draws you can chain up to 20 ren in
    a game.


    The best chance you can have at chaining ren is if you have four
    columns with three blocks in between, arranged in various ways.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
