  m_text: 'You can intuitively figure out which shapes can fit in to clear a line
    but here are some advanced tricks to help keep the chain going.


    With this
    pattern you could rotate the S in but if the next piece is a Z you can place
    it vertically which will set you up so you can rotate the Z into place.'
