  m_text: 'In competitive matches, garbage from opponents can come at any time and
    if you want to accumulate a lot of ren you will need to stack high. That''s why
    the best strategy is to build on the sides.


    Even if the stacks on the sides
    go over the top, as long as you can spawn a piece you will not top out.


    Here''s
    an example of an opening to set up for ren in the center:'
